Package com.jimmyselectronics.opeechee

package com.jimmyselectronics.opeechee
Welcome to Jimmy's Electronics, your one-stop shopping experience for high quality electronic components.

Our O-Pee-Chee line of electronic card readers is 100% free of cheap bubble gum, but 100% sure to satisfy all your card reading needs! Tap, insert, swipe: we support all the most common interaction modes.

Author:
Jimmy's Electronics LLP
